{"tid":2332667,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港愛情故事]將被拍成荷里活電影咁大件事冇人講？","createTime":"2020-12-19T19:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T10:33:22.000Z","uid":183058,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e18b7c587cde34cf7daa8635146f891d6706189","tid":2332667,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">荷里活拍《香港愛情故事》Nichkhun有份演　金像男配曾江強勢加盟</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzZAQvO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzZAQvO.jpg&h=738b3c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷里活電影《Hong Kong Love Story》（暫譯︰香港愛情故事）由Keoni Waxman執導，韓國男團2PM泰籍成員Nichkhun、美國港人男演員Byron Mann（文峰）主演，電影改編自Byron Mann的親身經歷，就連香港老戲骨金像獎最佳男配角曾江也有份加盟！不過該片與TVB熱播中的劇集《香港愛情故事》就一啲關係都冇。<br />\n<br />\n戲中將會講到兩名富家子弟Nichkhun和Byron Mann，來到香港尋找愛情，途中遇到一位波蘭的模特兒Dominica Kachlik，令到兩人的友誼受到考驗，似乎將會陷入三角戀中，而曾出演《新鐵金剛之不日殺機》、《藝伎回憶錄》、憑《竊聽風雲3》勇奪金像獎最佳男配角的曾江同樣有份演出。<br />\n<br />\n據知Nichkhun已經完成隔離，18日在香港開機拍攝，一眾演員都有在個人IG上分享合照，以及香港的特色街道。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：沈洛嘉<br />\n2020-12-19 22:05<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba17ae0cdc6248334d0f9364ed1ffcd8a932de3","tid":2332667,"uid":90660,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T21:22:19.000Z","msg":"tvb果套屌你老母有人睇嘅咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d51339c8b1b125b2bd1214419334718eb78626e","tid":2332667,"uid":194120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T22:16:59.000Z","msg":"曾江耳聽唔到影響講嘢,個染髮廣告聽佢講嘢已經有D一舊舊,仲拍戲?"},{"pid":"a76c2aecbfc1e8f574a130349f6a68fc9bd5fb61","tid":2332667,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T22:59:29.000Z","msg":"黃藍？"},{"pid":"79ae57e8ad56565ea672e762df44a1251f136073","tid":2332667,"uid":183058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ba17ae0cdc6248334d0f9364ed1ffcd8a932de3","tid":2332667,"uid":90660,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":